
Generally an enterprise level spring boot app contain

Gateway <--> service discovery
          |
          |
          V
    Spring security
          |
          V
 Any spring boot APP (a typical service)
          |
          |
          V
    Custom Filters
          |
          |
          V
    Custom Interceptors (logging & filtering incoming and outgoing requests and responses)
          |
          |
          V
     Validating incoming requests
          |
          |
          V
    Centralized logging ( configured with logback files etc..)
          |
          |
          V
     Custom Exceptions (Global exception handling)
